post_title: FS: Elmer Flick T206 partial back run - no longer available
post_content:
All prices are net to me and include postage.  I was putting together the back run but could never find a nice enough Hindu or any Old Mill for sale.  Let me know if any questions via PM or email.  An “I’ll take it” overrides an ongoing negotiation. I saved the PSA and SGC certs for these 4 cards that were freed from their holders. 

Piedmont 350 unholdered PSA4
Sweet Caporal 350, f25 unholdered SGC40
Sweet Caporal 150, f25 unholdered PSA4
Sweet Caporal 150, f30 raw (but really nice)
Sweet Caporal 350, f30 unholdered SGC50
